    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if they're holding the money hostage until things are fixed, does that mean they have a lot of power over the deal? it sounds kind of stressful that everything is just sitting there with a third party instead of being in my own account or the seller's account.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
